{"type": "article", "id": 2750, "title": "Mifland  2014 秋冬Weathered Patina 1998S 背包", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-10T08:04:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232523ny7sFi1V9mex6GPf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t制包品牌 Mifland 一直以其美式传统的手工制造工艺而闻名，日前 Mifland 正式带来 2014 秋冬Weathered Patina 1998S 系列。设计上主要是以优质的染色皮革为原料，通过精湛的制造工艺结合金属配件制作而成，再加上细节部分的做旧处理，更让该系列呈现出独一无二的美式复古质感。定价 399 美元，<a href=\"http://mifland.com/shop/standard-rucksack-1988s\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232520QzoUBkFlgv8LImiJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325210kwP1Xh6JNfetrOb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232521ZCOBcgF8zy0ksMQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232522P4O7wCJ50QpmvExX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}